{"tid":912612,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"26出發去東京 求行程指點","createTime":"2018-11-22T21:50:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T01:39:02.000Z","uid":52520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"610bbc2137ea9f6e3238d3abaca75d591a876f0e","tid":912612,"uid":52520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T21:50:18.000Z","msg":"26號1800機  落機就狗沖酒店放抵行李<br />\n<br />\n27號8點出門口去富山雨晴海岸 <br />\n（天氣好景靚就留到日落再出去市中心是旦搵地方訓）<br />\n    個景唔靚就改去相倉合掌村加睇下有冇機會落埋白川鄉望下之後就返返去東京<br />\n<br />\n28號  就去埼玉整宇宙玻璃（坂戶市）同埋去妻沼聖天山<br />\n<br />\n29號-3號主要去返東京玩     打算去迪士尼海洋 睇銀杏  卡比cafe 台場   其他未諗  <br />\n<br />\n巴打有冇好介紹/可修改既位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2adbbb482a96252780f656b9b2cbc24f061e99","tid":912612,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T21:55:10.000Z","msg":"食唔食壽司?"},{"pid":"a8fd222d2ea327678c84f3ff0f821ad065353ebf","tid":912612,"uid":52520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e2adbbb482a96252780f656b9b2cbc24f061e99","tid":912612,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T21:55:10.000Z","msg":"食唔食壽司?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T22:12:51.000Z","msg":"26-30既日子會食"},{"pid":"e7f9624e0ca8c91924de7e3233b46b48c6e44652","tid":912612,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8fd222d2ea327678c84f3ff0f821ad065353ebf","tid":912612,"uid":52520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e2adbbb482a96252780f656b9b2cbc24f061e99","tid":912612,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T21:55:10.000Z","msg":"食唔食壽司?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T22:12:51.000Z","msg":"26-30既日子會食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T22:14:24.000Z","msg":"坐bar枱同師傅邊食邊傾計"},{"pid":"fbf2d402dbaeb3f3db1c2332832bda0f10b1f722","tid":912612,"uid":52520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"